CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 17, 1966, pg. 18 reads: "The Freemans - The husband and wife teaching team of Glenn and Ida Freeman, is typical of many young couples today. Music and reading are among their hobbies.  Here Mrs. Freeman plays one of her husband's favorite songs."
TitMainTitle: Glenn Freeman, watching wife Ida playing piano, in Freeman home
